  <fr:p>We observe that <fr:link href="jms-002I.xml" title="Bottom and non-bottom elements are non-negatively generated" addr="jms-002I" type="local">every element of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> is non-negatively generated</fr:link>, so we <fr:link href="jms-0026.xml" title="Non-negatively generated basis yields positive generation" addr="jms-0026" type="local">may conclude</fr:link> that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="jms-0023.xml" title="Positively generated dcpos" addr="jms-0023" type="local">positively generated</fr:link>.</fr:p>
